<tr id="L335"><td><a href="#L335">335</a></td><td>MCCOY:  That's how we missed it. It passed from man to man through perspiration. Once in the bloodstream, it acts like alcohol, depresses the centres of judgment, self-control. Now get someone to the lab. Tell them the serum works, and start preparing more.</td></tr>

<tr id="L336"><td><a href="#L336">336</a></td><td>SULU:  Doc, will you let me out of here? I'm all right.</td></tr>

